p: We carry out parameter estimation and simulations as described in previous sections, for 85 strains of H1N1 influenza isolated in years other than 2009. This includes 15 strains isolated before 2000, 21 strains isolated between 2000 and 2008 (inclusive), and 49 strains isolated after 2009. We find that the trends identified in Fig 9 apply even for these strains; see supporting information S3 Fig.
